# Implementation Plan: Enrollment & Learning Flow (Phase 4 Continuation)

This plan details the design, files, and verification criteria for completing the remainder of Phase 4: **Enrollment Logic**, **Progress Tracking**, **Student Course Detail View**, and **Learning Player UI** (including video streaming, summary text, and interactive MCQ quizzes).

## User Review Required

> [!NOTE]
> - **Paid Course Enrollment (Mock)**: Paid courses will offer a mock instant-checkout session dialog in Phase 4. Real Stripe/PayPal gateway flows will be integrated in Phase 5.
> - **Curriculum Guardrails**: Non-enrolled students can view the syllabus (module/lesson titles) but cannot view secure assets like video URLs, text summaries, files, or quiz questions.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Backend: Enrollment & Progress APIs

#### [NEW] [serializers.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/payments/serializers.py)
Create serializers in the `payments` app:
- `EnrollmentSerializer`: Serializes student course enrollment and overall progress.
- `LessonProgressSerializer`: Handles completion status for individual lessons.

#### [MODIFY] [views.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/payments/views.py)
Implement DRF ViewSets:
- `EnrollmentViewSet`:
  - `POST /api/enrollments/`: Enrolls the logged-in student in a course. If free, activates instantly. If paid, prompts mock payment.
  - `GET /api/enrollments/`: Lists all courses the student is currently enrolled in.
  - `GET /api/enrollments/check/?course_id=<id>`: Checks if the user is enrolled in a specific course.
- `LessonProgressViewSet`:
  - `POST /api/progress/lessons/<lesson_id>/complete/`: Marks a lesson as completed for the student, updates progress timestamp, and updates the course's overall `progress_percent` on the `Enrollment` model.

#### [MODIFY] [urls.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/payments/urls.py)
Wire viewsets to routers and expose endpoints:
- `/api/enrollments/`
- `/api/progress/`

#### [MODIFY] [urls.py](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/backend/core/urls.py)
Register `payments.urls` in the project's root URLs configuration.

