### 2. Frontend: Course Details & Learning Player

#### [NEW] [CoursePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/frontend/src/pages/CoursePage.jsx) & [CoursePage.css](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/frontend/src/pages/CoursePage.css)
Student Course Detail Page:
- Displays course meta (title, desc, duration, level, price).
- Lists syllabus structure (modules/lessons list).
- Shows Enrollment button (or mock payment dialog for paid courses).
- If enrolled, displays overall completion progress bar and a "Continue Learning" button leading to the player.

#### [NEW] [LearningPlayer.jsx](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/frontend/src/pages/LearningPlayer.jsx) & [LearningPlayer.css](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/frontend/src/pages/LearningPlayer.css)
Visual Lesson Player & Quiz Board:
- Split layout:
  - Sidebar: Syllabus navigation showing lessons with checkboxes (checked if completed).
  - Main panel: Active content player.
- Dynamic loaders based on lesson type:
  - `VIDEO`: Custom player element using the secure stream link.
  - `DOCUMENT`: Beautiful markdown summary formatting.
  - `PDF`: Document viewer with file download/view access.
  - `QUIZ`: Interactive questionnaire. Renders MCQs one by one. Validates user answers, displays instant feedback, and computes final grade.
- Footer controls: "Mark as Complete" button, which calls the backend to check off progress and automatically selects the next lesson in the syllabus.

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/shans/CascadeProjects/Online_Education_Platform/frontend/src/App.jsx)
Register routes:
- `/courses/:courseId` -> `CoursePage`
- `/courses/:courseId/learn` -> `LearningPlayer`

