## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
Add assertions in `backend/courses/tests.py` or `backend/payments/tests.py`:
- Test that students can enroll in free courses instantly.
- Test that progress percentage scales correctly as lessons are completed.
- Test that video url / attachments are hidden from non-enrolled students.

### Manual Verification
- Log in as student, select a course, view detail page, click "Enroll".
- Enter the Learning Player, check off lessons, watch progress update.
- Submit a quiz, verify scoring, and advance to next lesson.
